Wikipedia

Articles English: Alexander Farnese, Duke of Parma

Alessandro Farnese, Duke of Parma and Piacenza, Governor of the Spanish Netherlands, was born 27 August 1545 in Rome to Ottavio Farnese (1524-1586) and Margaret of Austria (1522-1586) and died 3 December 1592 Arras of unspecified causes. He married Mary of Guimarães (1538-1577) 11 November 1565 JL .
